# Vendored skill deps are build artifacts — rebuilt via each skill's
# scripts/build.sh (webcrack node_modules incl. isolated-vm native addons;
# pure-python decompiler site dirs). Source (SKILL.md, scripts/*.py, run.mjs,
# package.json, package-lock.json, build.sh, *.version) is tracked; the manifest
# lives in rekit's registry.json + the generated skills-manifest.json.
skills/*/scripts/node_modules/
skills/*/scripts/site/
